text=(:nogroupheader:)%0aWelcome to the PmWiki Cookbook!  Here%0ayou will find PmWiki [[CookbookBasics|add-ons and descriptions]] of how to%0acustomize PmWiki in lots of different ways.%0a%0aようこそPmWiki Cookbookへ!%0aここで、様々な方法でPmWikiをカスタマイズする、PmWiki[[CookbookBasics|アドオンと記述]]を見つけられるでしょう。%0a%0a%25left bgcolor=#fff border='1px solid black' padding=3px%25'''Note:'''%0aThese are PmWiki 2.0 and 2.1 recipes.  See [[Cookbook-V1(.HomePage)]]%0afor PmWiki 0.6 and 1.0 recipes.%25%25%0a%0a%25left bgcolor=#fff border='1px solid black' padding=3px%25'''注:'''%0aこれらはPmWiki2.0と2.1のレシピです。0.6と1.0は[[Cookbook-V1(.HomePage)]]を参照してください%25%25%0a%0aFeel free to add your own contributions to the cookbook.%0aIf you want to write and distribute Cookbook recipes, see the cookbook [[module guidelines]]. %0aIn order to avoid duplication, make sure you check the archives of the [[http://search.gmane.org/search.php?group=gmane.comp.web.wiki.pmwiki.user|discussion list]] for keywords of what you want to implement.%0a%0aCookbookへのあなた自身の貢献を加えるのに遠慮は要りません｡%0aあなたがCookbookのレシピを書き, 配りたかったらCookbook [[module guidelines|モジュールガイドライン]]を見てください｡%0aまず重複を避けるために、実行したいことのキーワードで%0a[[http://search.gmane.org/search.php?group=gmane.comp.web.wiki.pmwiki.user|ディスカッションリスト]] %0aのアーカイブをチェックして下さい｡%0a%0aProposals and ideas for new features%0a(as opposed to existing solutions)%0ashould be added to the ''PmWiki Issue Tracking System''%0a([[PITS/PITS]]).%0a%0a(既存の解決に対する)新たな提案とアイディアは''PmWiki問題追跡システム''([[PITS/PITS]])に加えられるべきです。%0a%0a----%0a%0a!! Table of Contents%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#AdminTasks| Administrative Tasks ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#CMS| Content Management System Add-Ons ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Editing| Editing ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#FormTools| Form Tools ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Functions| Functional extensions ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Images| Images ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Insert| Insertions/Uploads ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Layout| Layout modifications ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Links| Links/Page handling ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Markup| Markup changes ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#MarkupWriting| Markup writing ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Menus| Menu Tools ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#PageNaming | Page Naming Schemes ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#PIM| Personal Information Management (PIM) ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#RSSTools| RSS Tools ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#Security| Security/Authentication ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#SystemTools| System Tools ]]%0a* [[Cookbook/Cookbook#WikiWiki| Wiki-to-Wiki Conversion Tools ]]%0a%0a!! 目次%0a* [[Cookbook#AdminTasks| 管理タスク ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#CMS| コンテンツ管理システムアドオン ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Editing| 編集]]%0a* [[Cookbook#FormTools| フォームツール ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Functions| 関数拡張 ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Images| 画像]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Insert| 挿入/アップロード ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Layout| レイアウト変更 ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Links| リンク/ページ操作 ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Markup| マークアップの変更 ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#MarkupWriting| マークアップ記述 ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Menus| メニューツール ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#PageNaming | ページネーミングスキーム ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#PIM| パーソナルな情報管理(PIM) ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#RSSTools| RSSツール ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#Security| セキュリティ/認証 ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#SystemTools| システムツール ]]%0a* [[Cookbook#WikiWiki| Wiki-Wiki変換ツール ]]%0a%0aSee also:%0a%0a* [[PageList | List of all Cookbook pages]] (alphabetical)%0a* [[Recent Changes]] - All Cookbook pages sorted by edit date.%0a* [[List of Bundles]] for examples of what recipes people use together%0a* [[Category| List of Categories]]%0a(:comment *an [[alternative listing]] -- this is not ready yet:)%0a%0aこちらも参照%0a%0a* [[PageList | Cookbookページの目次]] (アルファベット順)%0a* [[Recent Changes|変更履歴]] - 変更日時順%0a* [[List of Bundles]] for examples of what recipes people use together%0a* [[Category| カテゴリリスト]]%0a(:comment *an [[alternative listing]] -- this is not ready yet:)%0a%0a------%0a%0a!![[#AdminTasks]]Administrative Tasks%0a: [[AutoRestore|自動再構築]] %25dlcol%25 : 一定時間後にページを自動的に再構築%0a: [[Backup Pages|ページバックアップ]] : wiki.dディレクトリを圧縮ファイルにバックアップ%0a: [[Change Time Format|日時様式の変更]] : 日時フォーマット文字列やタイムゾーンを変更%0a